vbr": 4842.723, "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 79668241, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-1268469001969637v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by buelistic", "description": "You are not living in an objective world.\nYou are living inside your nervous system- regulated or unregulated\n\nNeuroscience studies ave discovered that over 90% of sensory data is filtered out before it ever reaches your conscious awareness. What you call “reality” is just your brain predicting what matters most for its safety &survival(this defense is built from past experiences, emotional memories, and expectation)\nLike I said, Two people can be in the same room, hear the same words, experience the same event… and process entirely different worlds.\n\nQuantum physics shows us why this matters.\nAt the subatomic level, particles do not exist as fixed objects. They exist as probabilities of existence. They exist as potential waves/frequencies until measured. Observation-aka your focus-isn’t passive. It forces reality to select. Then It collapses all those different possibilities into one form.\n\n⚡️Again! Remember Your thoughts are electrical signals traveling through neural networks.\n🧲Your emotions are magnetic fields generated by the heart & body.Together, they form a signal and it trains what your brain notices, what your body prepares for, and as a result trains the world to show which probabilities to bring to the surface of your experience.\nThis is why repetition works.\nThis is why visualization works.\nThis is why belief👉🏽when paired with emotional certainty👈🏽changes outcomes. Not because you’re “pretending.”But because the nervous system cannot distinguish between an experience vividly imagined and one physically lived. The body calibrates first. Reality follows.\n\n“Reality is merely an illusion, albeit a very persistent one.”\n-AAlbert Einstein\nThe Quanta 2.0 breaks this down precisely, what the world is, how to regulate your state while experiencing it, building coherence, and intentionally raising the probability of the life you want to experience. And once you understand the system, you stop asking for permission, you start directing outcomes.\n\nLink in bio.", "duration": 131.609, "timestamp": 1768259308, "uploader_id": "434229729", "uploader": "Quantum Vocalist", "channel": "buelistic", "like_count": 87500, "comment_count": 2313, "comments": [{"author": "thehomeofobsessivedreamers", "author_id": "18047142815", "id": "18104211034914436", "text": "💭", "timestamp": 1774893490}, {"author": "creativeben80", "author_id": "6998260566", "id": "18425364241190452", "text": "To create a new reality you must put in the repetition of that reality for the connection in neuroplasticity", "timestamp": 1774763762}, {"author": "aaron994305", "author_id": "42041384868", "id": "17932788696210559", "text": "G7", "timestamp": 1774732864}, {"author": "rosegoldplayaa", "author_id": "1585486742", "id": "17852380509641566", "text": "✅", "timestamp": 1774667912}, {"author": "deangough9", "author_id": "71353499243", "id": "18062434808357331", "text": "❤️❤️❤️❤️", "timestamp": 1774514611}, {"author": "kellh89", "author_id": "78025602774", "id": "18441495445119497", "text": "", "timestamp": 1774467822}, {"author": "kabet538", "author_id": "78125516998", "id": "17971663056008555", "text": "Very true🔥🔥", "timestamp": 1774449331}, {"author": "hyan_rigley", "author_id": "27130308", "id": "18040534526590933", "text": "Where’d you start", "timestamp": 1774397338}, {"author": "juliaslocketmusic", "author_id": "75976079615", "id": "18109810486692712", "text": "You just look so wise your eyes got the whole universe in them babe. Thank you for this message! It came as a perfect reminder to realign me at the perfect timing. Yay!!😊🙏", "timestamp": 1773691173}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/616226751_1283378510235974_8509940878819235864_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF6mjBBTocMG81r-o45h_ioRGAj-VBmr4duwOAM6EdWdnwd4iueZ0bXu5znlRw2Sss&_nc_ohc=7dYOHa8dOZsQ7kNvwHV8msA&_nc_gid=NUa50zZMR8Fjl6uH5LhMEQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af07uoaQzCfBUa06UchfHjIXQAqXbF9AohWXESEKuwyJ5g&oe=69D4C486&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/616226751_1283378510235974_8509940878819235864_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF6mjBBTocMG81r-o45h_ioRGAj-VBmr4duwOAM6EdWdnwd4iueZ0bXu5znlRw2Sss&_nc_ohc=7dYOHa8dOZsQ7kNvwHV8msA&_nc_gid=NUa50zZMR8Fjl6uH5LhMEQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af07uoaQzCfBUa06UchfHjIXQAqXbF9AohWXESEKuwyJ5g&oe=69D4C486&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/616226751_1283378510235974_8509940878819235864_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF6mjBBTocMG81r-o45h_ioRGAj-VBmr4duwOAM6EdWdnwd4iueZ0bXu5znlRw2Sss&_nc_ohc=7dYOHa8dOZsQ7kNvwHV8msA&_nc_gid=NUa50zZMR8Fjl6uH5LhMEQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af07uoaQzCfBUa06UchfHjIXQAqXbF9AohWXESEKuwyJ5g&oe=69D4C486&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 1080, "height": 1917, "id": "2", "resolution": "1080x1917"}], "http_headers"